headline: Assessing Prologis (PLD) Valuation After Strong Multi Year Shareholder Returns
summary: Recent share price gains for Prologis (PLD) have put fresh attention on the logistics real estate owner as investors weigh its current valuation against recent returns and underlying earnings and revenue figures. See our latest analysis for Prologis. The recent 1 month share price return of 6.81% and 3 month share price return of 8.39% put Prologis’ latest move into context, with a 1 year total shareholder return of 18.94% and 5 year total shareholder return of 45.33%.
